{"tid":40463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[小明去左邊?] 中聯辦：在北京參加中央經濟工作會議","createTime":"2016-12-15T08:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T09:07:22.000Z","uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccd0a752e33c8c6dd2692353e0fc7f11d6321d64","tid":40463,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"中聯辦主任張曉明原獲邀出席今晚的政府人員協會聚餐，但他今晚不會出席。 <br />\n<br />\n中聯辦表示，張曉明正身在北京，出席中央經濟工作會議。 <br />\n<br />\n據新華社昨天報道，會議即日召開，中央領導層回顧今年中國經濟表現，並制定明年經濟計劃，會議預計本周完結。 <br />\n<br />\n張曉明上星期六亦沒有如往年一樣，出席工展會開幕。"},{"pid":"7378519d96f57bf0512e4d8d7c220eea5e2081d8","tid":40463,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"搭錯火車"},{"pid":"9524da8758aca70218ed864b880d338b17591488","tid":40463,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:29:05.000Z","msg":"即係照肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9606e2e00b180f0279938da836268a3c22154e53","tid":40463,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"成報早兩日都話佢係北京"},{"pid":"5cfeda43484742d44af1c609e7260cd8721641bf","tid":40463,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"會唔會返唔到落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460a7bbce056a3168cd657ed6028604b8ecfa03c","tid":40463,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:55:35.000Z","msg":"明仔個位關經濟撚事，作都作好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a783b13ae40f0eefa507cef5ca25fd55e30c6a7a","tid":40463,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}